{"tid":676210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【每年返溫哥華探親】外婆冇見過何雁詩 鄭俊弘：冇催婚","createTime":"2018-05-24T07:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T07:08:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"955e7312cb18360820f45a95bfecd3061044aec1","tid":676210,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"鄭俊弘今日喺北角出席慈善活動，即場表演，同埋派褔袋俾老人家，現場有吳君如父母及葉尚華夫婦。鄭俊弘話今日係同阿媽出席活動，佢平時鍾意同長者傾偈從中學習：「以前阿公未走，我會聽佢講以前由鄉下去金山生活，跟住做廚房，仲會講第2次世界大戰嘅事，佢好勁，喺外國生活及開枝散葉。」<br />\n<br />\n現時外婆居住溫哥華，鄭俊弘會每年探訪，外婆知佢同何雁詩拍拖，但冇催婚，鄭俊弘話：「外婆只係會叫我注意身體健康，叫我飲少啲凍嘢。」問到未來孫新抱有冇見面？佢話：「冇，未有機會。」稍後，外婆會回港探望曾孫。另外，鄭俊弘後日出發到馬來西亞工作，女友唔會同行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180524/large/1527145331_ae8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F1527145331_ae8b.jpg&h=9481b934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180524/58231691?_ga=2.69393872.1733420237.1526448162-1567888096.1524463134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58231691%3F_ga%3D2.69393872.1733420237.1526448162-1567888096.1524463134&d=l%2Bs1Dl%2BLTlmF99EQBzEaTxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=0a3dc6c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58231691%3F_ga%3D2.69393872.1733420237.1526448162-1567888096.1524463134&h=3f24664e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180524/58231691?_ga=2.69393872.1733420237.1526448162-1567888096.1524463134</a>"},{"pid":"9fc029bb3a4b36a26f086a980d590ad522a4eb60","tid":676210,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T07:49:40.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"82b3446a254dba21891d8d442a46a8a8c7f26779","tid":676210,"uid":39439,"like":0,"dislike":0,